data.enText: a sea animal (a mammal ) that looks like a large fish with a pointed mouth. Dolphins are very intelligent and often friendly towards humans. There are several types of dolphin .

tr: any of various small toothed whales with a beaklike snout
large slender food and game fish widely distributed in warm seas (especially around Hawaii)

value.def: A dolphin is a mammal which lives in the sea and looks like a large fish with a pointed mouth.
